cf.lukasheinzl.lexing

Interface TokenType


  • public interface TokenType
    This is the interface for all TokenTypes. It contains only one type: EMPTY. All other required types have to be supplied from the user. These types should be enums implementing this interface.
    Author:
    Lukas Heinzl
